                <h1>NAS debate reveals faculty divisions on curriculum, ideology</h1>
                
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/betsy-kaiser">Betsy Kaiser</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">October 3, 1990 | 11:21pm EDT</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
